  "response": "As an AI, I don't have personal experiences, but I can share some impactful and memorable quotes from teachers that are often praised for their wisdom and encouragement:\n\n1. \"Mistakes are proof that you are trying.\"\n2. \"The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.\" \u2014 Eleanor Roosevelt\n3. \"Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world.\" \u2014 Nelson Mandela\n4. \"Don't be afraid to ask questions. It's how you learn.\"\n5. \"Believe in yourself. You are capable of great things.\"\n6. \"Every challenge you face is an opportunity to grow.\"\n7. \"Your attitude, not your aptitude, will determine your altitude.\" \u2014 Zig Ziglar\n8. \"Learning is a lifelong journey; embrace it with curiosity and enthusiasm.\"\n\nSuch statements can inspire and motivate students to strive for their best and embrace the learning process.",
